      "settings": {
        "code": "<style>\n/* ============================================================\n   ampy-main-cta.css — Ampy \"Main CTA\"-block\n   FluentSnippets-leverans (WordPress/Bricks). FORMAT ONLY.\n   Källa: Main_CTA/index.html <style> (LÅST design, rev 2).\n   Inga färger/gradienter/skuggor/animationer/geometri ändrade —\n   endast (1) wrapper-scopad under .ampy-mcta, (2) rem→px, (3)\n   viewport-@media → @container, (4) self-hostad Outfit.\n\n   HTML: <section class=\"mcta\"> → <section class=\"ampy-mcta\">.\n   Alla mcta__*-klasser oförändrade.\n\n   rem→px (blocket antog html{font-size:62.5%} = 1rem/10px;\n   WP-root är oftast 16px → alla rem konverterade till px så\n   blocket är oberoende av temats root):\n     2.8rem→28px  4rem→40px  2.4rem→24px(i clamp)\n     1.6rem→16px  1.53rem→15.3px(i clamp)  1.8rem→18px\n     1.5rem→15px  2.6rem→26px  1.2rem→12px(i clamp)  3.2rem→32px\n     2.4rem→24px  3rem→30px  2.2rem→22px\n   vw-termer i clamp() = viewport-enheter, oberoende av root → verbatim.\n\n   @container: wrappern får container-type:inline-size + container-name,\n   och de fyra viewport-breakpointarna (1300 / 768–1024 / 767 / 360)\n   körs som @container så blocket bryter mot SIN EGEN bredd i smala\n   Bricks-kolumner, inte mot browserbredden. Feature-queries\n   (forced-colors / print / prefers-reduced-motion) + @supports är\n   INTE viewport-queries → kvar som @media/@supports, bara om-scopade.\n   ============================================================ */\n\n/* ---- Self-hostad Outfit (ingen Google Fonts) --------------------\n   Bas-URL är filtrerbar i PHP (ampy_mcta_font_base); CSS pekar på\n   standard uploads-sökväg. Vikter: 300 (body/p), 400 (g-row),\n   500 (rubrik/knapp), 700 (5,0). font-display:swap. */\n@font-face{\n  font-family:'Outfit';font-style:normal;font-weight:300;font-display:swap;\n  src:url('/wp-content/uploads/ampy/fonts/Outfit-Light.woff2') format('woff2'),\n      url('/wp-content/uploads/ampy/fonts/Outfit-Light.woff') format('woff');\n}\n@font-face{\n  font-family:'Outfit';font-style:normal;font-weight:400;font-display:swap;\n  src:url('/wp-content/uploads/ampy/fonts/Outfit-Regular.woff2') format('woff2'),\n      url('/wp-content/uploads/ampy/fonts/Outfit-Regular.woff') format('woff');\n}\n@font-face{\n  font-family:'Outfit';font-style:normal;font-weight:500;font-display:swap;\n  src:url('/wp-content/uploads/ampy/fonts/Outfit-Medium.woff2') format('woff2'),\n      url('/wp-content/uploads/ampy/fonts/Outfit-Medium.woff') format('woff');\n}\n@font-face{\n  font-family:'Outfit';font-style:normal;font-weight:700;font-display:swap;\n  src:url('/wp-content/uploads/ampy/fonts/Outfit-Bold.woff2') format('woff2'),\n      url('/wp-content/uploads/ampy/fonts/Outfit-Bold.woff') format('woff');\n}\n\n/* ---- Root wrapper: scopade tokens + container + font-bas + sektion-ram ---- */\n.ampy-mcta{\n  /* scopade custom properties (var :root) */\n  --teal:hsl(171 100% 33%);\n  --teal-bright:hsl(171 95% 41%);\n  --blue:hsl(189 43% 56%);\n  --midnight:hsl(237 69% 12%);\n  --ink:#363636;\n  --section-bg:#f5f9ff;\n  --radius-l:clamp(16px, 1.4vw, 20px);\n  --radius-m:16px;\n\n  /* container-kontext: inre breakpoints följer blockets bredd, ej viewporten */\n  container-type:inline-size;\n  container-name:ampy-mcta;\n\n  /* font-bas (var body) */\n  font-family:'Outfit',system-ui,sans-serif;font-weight:300;\n  color:var(--ink);\n  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;\n\n  /* sektion-ram (var .mcta) */\n  background:var(--section-bg);\n  padding:clamp(28px,4vw,56px) clamp(16px,3vw,40px);\n  display:flex;justify-content:center;\n}\n.ampy-mcta,\n.ampy-mcta *,\n.ampy-mcta *::after,\n.ampy-mcta *::before{box-sizing:border-box}\n.ampy-mcta img{max-width:100%;display:block}\n.ampy-mcta a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit}\n\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__card{\n  position:relative;overflow:hidden;\n  width:min(1280px,100%);\n  background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius-l);\n  box-shadow:0 0 16px rgba(190,190,190,.4);\n  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 400px;gap:clamp(24px,3vw,48px);\n  padding:clamp(28px,3.2vw,48px) clamp(28px,4.5vw,72px);\n  align-items:center;\n}\n/* bg-vågen (Vector-3) — bakom allt, förankrad nere-höger som i originalet */\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__bgwave{\n  position:absolute;right:clamp(28px,4.5vw,72px);bottom:clamp(28px,3.2vw,48px);\n  width:44%;height:auto;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;\n}\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__text{position:relative;z-index:1;min-width:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px}\n\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__h{\n  margin:0;font-size:clamp(28px,1.25vw + 24px,40px);font-weight:500;line-height:1.1;\n  color:var(--midnight);letter-spacing:-.01em;\n}\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__h .grad{\n  color:var(--teal-bright); /* fallback om text-clip ej stöds */\n  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--teal-bright) 15%,var(--blue) 85%);\n  -webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;\n  -webkit-box-decoration-break:clone;box-decoration-break:clone; /* jämn gradient över radbrytning (Safari-söm) */\n  font-weight:inherit;\n}\n/* resiliens: gradient-text får aldrig försvinna om bakgrundsgrafik nollas */\n@supports not ((-webkit-background-clip:text) or (background-clip:text)){\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__h .grad{-webkit-text-fill-color:currentColor;background:none;color:var(--teal-bright)}\n}\n@media (forced-colors:active){\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__h .grad{-webkit-text-fill-color:currentColor;background:none;color:CanvasText}\n}\n@media print{\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__h .grad{-webkit-text-fill-color:currentColor;background:none;color:#090b32}\n}\n/* forcerad brytning (\"...inom 60\" / \"sekunder!\") ENDAST på bred desktop där\n   vänsterkolumnen rymmer rad 1 — under 1300px sköter naturlig brytning det\n   utan orphan (verifierat: 1120px ger rent 2-radigt \"...inom\" / \"60 sekunder!\") */\n.ampy-mcta .br-d{display:none}\n@container ampy-mcta (min-width:1300px){.ampy-mcta .br-d{display:inline}}\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__p{\n  margin:0;font-size:clamp(16px,.21vw + 15.3px,18px);line-height:1.6;\n  max-width:52ch;text-align:left;\n}\n\n/* ============ RING-CTA ============\n   Blockets ENDA CTA. Blå brand-gradient, mjuk navy-text, vit chip med\n   puls-ring, lur optiskt centrerad. Mobil: fullbredd, text vänster /\n   ikon höger (live-blockets grammatik); desktop: chip vänster. */\n/* CTA + betyg-rad staplade (betyget UNDER knappen, som mobilen) — samma på desktop. */\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__action{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;margin-top:8px}\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__cta{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px}\n.ampy-mcta .btn-ring{\n  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;\n  min-height:58px;border-radius:var(--radius-m);\n  font-size:16px;font-weight:500;line-height:1;white-space:nowrap;\n  color:hsl(237 35% 24%);\n  transition:transform .16s ease, box-shadow .16s ease, filter .16s ease;\n}\n.ampy-mcta .btn-ring{\n  gap:14px;padding:11px 30px 11px 12px;\n  background:linear-gradient(120deg,#b6f2ff 0%,#5eb1bf 100%);\n  box-shadow:\n    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.55),\n    0 2px 4px rgba(9,11,50,.06),\n    0 10px 26px -6px rgba(94,177,191,.55);\n}\n.ampy-mcta .btn-ring:hover{\n  transform:translateY(-1.5px);\n  filter:saturate(1.08) brightness(1.02);\n  box-shadow:\n    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.55),\n    0 3px 6px rgba(9,11,50,.07),\n    0 16px 34px -8px rgba(94,177,191,.65);\n}\n.ampy-mcta .btn-ring:active{transform:translateY(0);filter:saturate(1.05)}\n.ampy-mcta .btn-ring:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--midnight);outline-offset:3px} /* midnight = ≥3:1 fokuskontrast mot ljus yta (var --blue ~2,5:1) */\n/* forced-colors (Windows högkontrast): gradienten strippas → synlig kant så knapp-affordansen överlever */\n@media (forced-colors:active){.ampy-mcta .btn-ring{border:1px solid ButtonText}}\n.ampy-mcta .btn-ring__chip{\n  position:relative;flex:0 0 auto;\n  width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;\n  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\n  background:rgba(255,255,255,.92);color:hsl(237 35% 24%);\n  box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(9,11,50,.14);\n}\n.ampy-mcta .btn-ring__chip::after{\n  content:\"\";position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:50%;\n  box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(255,255,255,.65);\n  animation:mctaRing 2.8s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.4,1) infinite;\n}\n@keyframes mctaRing{\n  0%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(255,255,255,.65)}\n  55%{box-shadow:0 0 0 9px rgba(255,255,255,0)}\n  100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(255,255,255,0)}\n}\n@media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){\n  .ampy-mcta .btn-ring__chip::after{animation:none}\n  .ampy-mcta .btn-ring,.ampy-mcta .btn-ring:hover{transition:none;transform:none}\n}\n.ampy-mcta .btn-ring svg{flex:0 0 auto}\n/* optisk mikro-nudge: luren en gnutta ner-vänster i chipen */\n.ampy-mcta .btn-ring__chip svg{transform:translate(-1px,1px)}\n\n/* proof-raden — REN inline-rad UNDER CTA:n (ingen box/container, ägar-önskan):\n   färgad Google-G · \"5,0 på Google\" · fem GULA stjärnor. Diskret underline på\n   hover (länk till recensioner). Hela raden = EN länk, 44px hit-area. */\n.ampy-mcta .g-row{\n  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;\n  min-height:44px;padding:6px 0;\n  font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:var(--midnight);line-height:1;\n}\n.ampy-mcta .g-row:hover .g-label{text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px}\n.ampy-mcta .g-row:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--midnight);outline-offset:3px} /* midnight = tydlig fokusring mot ljus yta */\n.ampy-mcta .g-row .g-icon{display:block;flex:0 0 auto;width:17px;height:17px}\n.ampy-mcta .g-row .g-label{display:block;white-space:nowrap}\n.ampy-mcta .g-row strong{font-weight:700}           /* \"5,0\" fet, \"på Google\" ärver 400 */\n.ampy-mcta .g-row .stars{display:inline-flex;gap:3px;flex:0 0 auto}\n.ampy-mcta .g-row .stars svg{width:15px;height:15px;fill:#FBBC04;display:block} /* gula stjärnor (ägar-önskan) */\n\n/* bildblocket — baslinjens geometri: kolumn 400px, bilden 80 % bredd,\n   flex-end, samma boxproportion som originalbilden (320×366), radius,\n   overlay-vågen nere-höger över bildens nedre hörn */\n/* OBS: overflow:hidden är BORTTAGET här — det klippte fotots fallskugga.\n   Vågen behöver inte längre klippas (den ligger inom media horisontellt och\n   är nu bottom:0, ingen 1px-blödning), och fotot bär sin egen border-radius. */\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__media{\n  margin:0;position:relative;z-index:1;align-self:stretch;\n  display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:flex-end;\n  min-height:366px;\n}\n/* croppen: fönstret täcker huvudtopp (~16 %) med luft ovanför NER TILL\n   ampy-loggan på tröjan (~86 %) — samma framing på alla enheter */\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__media .photo{\n  display:block;\n  width:80%;height:auto;aspect-ratio:320/366;object-fit:cover;object-position:50% 46%;\n  border-radius:var(--radius-l);\n  /* EN hårfin ljusring (border, INTE inset box-shadow — inset renderas ej på <img>)\n     + EN mjuk, riktad fallskugga i midnatt så porträttet lyfter från vita kortet.\n     Negativ spread håller sidfotavtrycket smalt → ryms inom kortets padding,\n     som har overflow:hidden. */\n  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.55);\n  box-shadow:0 18px 40px -20px rgba(9,11,50,.26);\n}\n.ampy-mcta .mcta__wave{\n  position:absolute;right:0;bottom:0;width:50%;height:auto;z-index:2;pointer-events:none;\n}\n\n/* tablett 768–1024: FLUID bildkolumn (aldrig bredare än texten) + lugnare rubrik\n   — löser iPad Mini/Air där fast 340px svälte textkolumnen till 3-radig rubrik */\n@container ampy-mcta (max-width:1024px) and (min-width:768px){\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__card{\n    grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) clamp(260px,34vw,320px);\n    gap:clamp(20px,3vw,32px);\n    padding:clamp(28px,3vw,36px) clamp(28px,3.5vw,40px);\n  }\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__bgwave{right:32px;bottom:28px;width:38%}\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__media{min-height:0}\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__h{font-size:clamp(26px,2.2vw + 12px,32px)}\n}\n@container ampy-mcta (max-width:767px){\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__card{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:20px;padding:20px 20px 28px}\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__bgwave{display:none}\n  /* bild-TAK på CONTAINERN (inte motivet): aldrig fullbredd i stackat läge\n     (annars gigantisk vid 450–767) + en gnutta smalare på telefon (ägar-önskan).\n     Vågen är barn till containern → linjerar då mot bildkanten. */\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__media{order:-1;align-self:center;justify-content:center;min-height:0;width:min(92%,360px);margin-inline:auto}\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__media .photo{width:100%;aspect-ratio:320/366;object-position:50% 46%}\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__wave{width:60%}\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__text{align-items:center}\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__h{text-align:center;font-size:clamp(24px,5.5vw,30px);line-height:1.16}\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__p{text-align:center}\n  /* mobil: CTA + betyg-rad centrerade, fullbredd (oförändrat läge) */\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__action{align-items:center;width:100%}\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__cta{width:100%;flex-direction:column;gap:12px}\n  /* mobil: text vänster / ikon höger (live-blockets grammatik) */\n  .ampy-mcta .btn-ring{width:100%;flex-direction:row-reverse;justify-content:space-between;padding:11px 12px 11px 22px}\n  .ampy-mcta .g-row{align-self:center}\n}\n@container ampy-mcta (max-width:360px){\n  .ampy-mcta .mcta__h{font-size:22px}\n}\n</style>\n<section class=\"ampy-mcta\">\n  <div class=\"mcta__card\">\n    <img class=\"mcta__bgwave\" src=\"assets/Vector-3.svg\" alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"652\" height=\"273\">\n\n    <div class=\"mcta__text\">\n      <h2 class=\"mcta__h\">Prata med en elektriker <span class=\"grad\">inom 60<br class=\"br-d\"> sekunder!</span></h2>\n      <p class=\"mcta__p\">Känn dig trygg med kunnig hjälp, precis när du behöver den. Prata direkt med en erfaren elektriker som lyssnar på ditt behov och guidar dig till en säker, smidig lösning.</p>\n      <div class=\"mcta__action\">\n      <div class=\"mcta__cta\">\n        <a class=\"btn-ring\" href=\"tel:+46102657979\">\n          <span class=\"btn-ring__chip\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <svg width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0.45 -0.49 19 20\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M11.9 4.2c.8.2 1.5.6 2 1.1.6.6 1 1.3 1.1 2.1M11.9.8c1.6.2 3.1 1 4.2 2.2 1.2 1.2 1.9 2.7 2.1 4.4M17.4 14.1v2.5c0 .5-.2.9-.5 1.2-.3.3-.8.5-1.2.4-2.4-.3-4.8-1.2-6.8-2.6-1.9-1.3-3.5-3-4.8-5-1.3-2.2-2.2-4.6-2.4-7.2 0-.5.1-.9.4-1.2.3-.3.7-.5 1.2-.5h2.4c.8 0 1.5.6 1.6 1.4.1.8.3 1.6.6 2.3.2.6.1 1.3-.4 1.8l-1 1c1.1 2.1 2.8 3.8 4.7 5l1-1c.5-.5 1.2-.6 1.8-.4.7.3 1.5.5 2.3.6.8.1 1.4.8 1.4 1.7Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n          </span>\n          Ring 010-265 79 79\n        </a>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"g-row\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Ampy/@59.3576299,17.9842061,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x2bec1ce5c4ed9ce9:0xfce1752e84a1bfee!8m2!3d59.3576272!4d17.986781!16s%2Fg%2F11ypjy9rrm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"5,0 på Google – Ampys betyg, 5 av 5 stjärnor. Läs recensionerna (öppnas i ny flik)\">\n        <svg class=\"g-icon\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 48 48\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill=\"#FFC107\" d=\"M43.6 20.1H42V20H24v8h11.3C33.7 32.7 29.2 36 24 36c-6.6 0-12-5.4-12-12s5.4-12 12-12c3.1 0 5.9 1.2 8 3l5.7-5.7C34.2 6.1 29.3 4 24 4 13 4 4 13 4 24s9 20 20 20 20-9 20-20c0-1.3-.1-2.6-.4-3.9z\"/><path fill=\"#FF3D00\" d=\"m6.3 14.7 6.6 4.8C14.7 15.1 19 12 24 12c3.1 0 5.9 1.2 8 3l5.7-5.7C34.2 6.1 29.3 4 24 4 16.3 4 9.7 8.3 6.3 14.7z\"/><path fill=\"#4CAF50\" d=\"M24 44c5.2 0 9.9-2 13.4-5.2l-6.2-5.2C29.2 35.1 26.7 36 24 36c-5.2 0-9.6-3.3-11.3-8l-6.5 5C9.5 39.6 16.2 44 24 44z\"/><path fill=\"#1976D2\" d=\"M43.6 20.1H42V20H24v8h11.3c-.8 2.2-2.2 4.2-4.1 5.6l6.2 5.2C41.4 34.8 44 29.9 44 24c0-1.3-.1-2.6-.4-3.9z\"/></svg>\n        <span class=\"g-label\"><strong>5,0</strong> på Google</span>\n        <span class=\"stars\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"m12 2 3.1 6.3 6.9 1-5 4.9 1.2 6.9L12 17.8 5.8 21l1.2-6.9-5-4.9 6.9-1z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"m12 2 3.1 6.3 6.9 1-5 4.9 1.2 6.9L12 17.8 5.8 21l1.2-6.9-5-4.9 6.9-1z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"m12 2 3.1 6.3 6.9 1-5 4.9 1.2 6.9L12 17.8 5.8 21l1.2-6.9-5-4.9 6.9-1z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"m12 2 3.1 6.3 6.9 1-5 4.9 1.2 6.9L12 17.8 5.8 21l1.2-6.9-5-4.9 6.9-1z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"m12 2 3.1 6.3 6.9 1-5 4.9 1.2 6.9L12 17.8 5.8 21l1.2-6.9-5-4.9 6.9-1z\"/></svg>\n        </span>\n      </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <figure class=\"mcta__media\">\n      <img class=\"photo\" src=\"assets/edvin.webp\" alt=\"Edvin, elektriker på Ampy\" width=\"933\" height=\"1400\" fetchpriority=\"high\">\n      <img class=\"mcta__wave\" src=\"assets/overlay.svg\" alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"277\" height=\"100\">\n    </figure>\n  </div>\n</section>",
        "executeCode": false
      },
      "label": "Main CTA (kodblock — pixel-troget fallback)"
    }
  ],
